{"tid":1747831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從來未見過建制派咁驚輸 出盡所有那渣手段干預選舉","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:17.000Z","uid":11454,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62fa4a93d428929247f3a27e2f1e490b51db0d2e","tid":1747831,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"掌心雷，種票呢啲基本唔再講<br />\n<br />\n改票站地點，威脅改投票時間，搵人扮中立𠝹票，取消選民登記名冊，威逼利誘，出盡所有手段去拎票，前所未見！<br />\n<br />\n聽日我唔係要泛民贏， <br />\n我係要建制輸，要佢輸到仆街！<br />\n<br />\n所有撞區嘅今晚要搞掂佢！<br />\n一個區都唔可以少！<br />\n<br />\n對付中共機器，唔理你係咩野人，邊一派<br />\n只要你嘅敵人係建制，中共就係同路人！<br />\n<br />\n機會只有一次唔好再戇鳩鳩投白票！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"4f6f3a85fd6f008e713821060882e821d9d1910e","tid":1747831,"uid":11454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"啱啱仲要係CCTVB賣廣告<br />\n真係驚輸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準時7:30去投票！"},{"pid":"6111afe804e68dfb4e579e00983412392b4d4531","tid":1747831,"uid":269773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:41:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b6d8d102eeb62e8c19aa13f36793c1b2a4cf5f2","tid":1747831,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"仲有呢兩日清晒所有連儂牆！<br />\n連啲偏遠地區都清！<br />\n朝早貼夜晚清，從未試過咁有效率！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0d2e2706adb23ff2a3ad02d31c0127896af5a0","tid":1747831,"uid":12994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我心底裡都知個個都做唔到野 <br />\n但我都唔想建制贏！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"47fd4265c4d0bf54cfcb228c36aef7033645cb73","tid":1747831,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b0d2e2706adb23ff2a3ad02d31c0127896af5a0","tid":1747831,"uid":12994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我心底裡都知個個都做唔到野 <br 